{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "c0ad4e78-8495-4f99-a28a-17cc9448d9be",
    "name": "I10: Nights of the Dead",
    "sceneId": "1c60250c-dab6-4aaa-aaeb-b7f4203ccb9d",
    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "48459e6f-186b-4766-9a29-3ffdd1c77c69",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "1dbf20d1-fbe1-4c60-bdd1-10193b7c2a55",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "f0f8612e-2847-4db5-b111-a6fd5804d401",
                            "text": "Ask About Ghosts",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "81e001b3-9eda-430d-9630-2323165cc8d9",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "So what are ghosts really? Are they just dead people that didn't get into Hades?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f3d2bc8c-f762-43af-b3a5-4a030d835862",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Some ghosts are the souls of those who die with unfulfilled needs - unrequited love, an unjust death, an unfinished goal... Some ghosts cannot find rest until their bodies are properly buried.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0266129c-3a9b-49c9-a0e4-bda1e3a62700",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "A few ghosts love too much or hate too deeply to leave this world. There are some ghosts who want to help the living. There are many different reasons why ghosts cannot find peace.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2f806228-bf45-41f6-b429-d053297d60c7",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "The ghosts in this castle will not harm you. I cannot say the same for some of the ghosts outside of the castle walls.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "86e25ac3-a721-47a6-bbb1-d12b06a125c1",
                            "text": "Talk About Nights of the Dead",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "aa6182fd-0d65-4e7d-8ce4-b015bcc657cb",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "Is it true that other lands don't have ghosts wandering around on the Nights of the Dead?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e515892a-5a92-4f31-8cf6-38353215e40c",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "While they celebrate the Nights of the Dead on the island of Marete and other places, I have never seen a ghost during the event elsewhere. Something about the magic of this land empowers ghosts to manifest.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "bbe19489-529b-4b78-8bf9-e8f12d8f13a8",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "Is this a good thing or a bad thing, the appearance of so many ghosts?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a7bff9f4-bc86-4d5e-80ae-11d5dfeaf72c",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "That's a very good question, Shawn. I just don't have a good answer yet.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "5455a96e-d568-4ccb-97ac-a439071c4f2a",
                            "text": "Flirt With Moira",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "fd7979a4-8bf0-4019-9907-790e389b83d4",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "amount": "1",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3d288d35-e375-4f6d-96a6-e3e2b1cb7e4f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "You know, you and I could walk around the castle later tonight to make sure that all the ghosts here are happy ones.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "705c11dd-43e3-46c7-8f4c-8e4cc7ba8bd4",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Thank you for the offer, but I think it would be more useful for me to do that by myself. I get the impression that you would be distracted from the ghosts.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d2d9c513-b662-4a3a-bafa-4f8ef4b40d52",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "Well, you are more attractive than the ghosts are.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "bb467581-f750-4e67-8ec2-9018bf691c96",
                            "text": "Goodbye",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.onceOnly",
                                    "id": "3a0b7b6f-22f1-41cc-8678-e056a5af953d",
                                    "nodes": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                            "id": "de371c2c-4cd8-40b3-8ae3-cfd924cae0de",
                                            "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                            "amount": "1",
                                            "change": "1",
                                            "notify": true
                                        }
                                    ]
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "20e32d17-041d-4dda-bf20-3f3f3195059c",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "See you later... don't let the ghosties get you!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "50292a53-6d8f-4e49-bc20-bee45da41385",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Have a good evening and a good Night of the Dead.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.endScript"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}